==== ENTRY 4 ====
HEADWORD: Gilt
<hw>Gilt</hw>, <pos>n.</pos> <sn>1.</sn> <def>Gold, or that which
resembles gold, laid on the surface of a thing; gilding.</def>
<rj><au>Shak.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>Money.</def> <mark>[Obs.]</mark> ⟦ldquo⟧The
<xex>gilt</xex> of France.⟦rdquo⟧ <rj><au>Shak.</au></rj></p>

